 <Description>
 <![CDATA[
This program detects all the cameras attached to all the installed
Matrox systems and starts grabbing from them using MdigProcess().<br /><br />
<b>Features include:</b><br /><br />
- Displaying multiple live streams from multiple boards.<br />
- No tearing video output.<br />
- Low latency video output.<br />
- Live camera addition and removal.<br />
- Changing the display between windowed and full screen mode.<br />
- Changing grab buffer pixel formats.<br />
- Activating encoding on a live stream.<br />
- Activating image processing on a live stream.<br />
- Displaying the Feature browser so that the user can control the digitizer<br />
  and camera settings.<br />
]]>
</Description>
